These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, begonia, aconite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, august
1. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Flower   | aconite | poppy | begonia |
| Birthday    | may    | august | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
House: wooden, colonial, victorian
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, soy-milk
1. the wooden house is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| House       | colonial | victorian | wooden |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | fanta     | water        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, spinach, kiwi
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, game, baccarat
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Food         | kiwi     | spinach | cucumber |
| Cigar   | game | bongani     | baccarat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, purple, apricot
There 3 different types of food: avocado, papaya, cranberry
1. the person who likes purple is the person eating papaya##1
2. the person who likes green is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person who likes purple is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Color   | apricot | purple  | green  |
| Food         | avocado  | papaya | cranberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, van
3 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, snake
1. the person driving the van is between the person driving the airplane and the owner of the goat##2
2. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Transport         | airplane   | van | bike    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | snake     | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, gospel
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, quad-bike
1. the fan of d&b is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | gospel | d&b   |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | bike    | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
House: tower, cottage, gothic-revival
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, poppy
1. the cottage house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the tower house is between the person who growspoppy and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the tower house is on the left of the cottage house##1
4. the person who growslily is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| House   | gothic-revival | tower | cottage |
| Flower           | bellflower         | lily         | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, rock, classical
City: prague, boston, rome
1. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to boston and the fan of r&b##2
2. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | classical | r&b |
| City    | boston    | prague | rome     |

