.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, disaster
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, ivory, lilac
1. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | scientific  | martial-arts  |
| Color         | lilac | ivory | green |

