.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, cat, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, tram, boat
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Pet   | pony    | rat      | cat |
| Transport       | tram | boat | airplane   |

