.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, scientific
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, argentine, french
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the thai is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the french is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | scientific | mystery |
| Nationality   | argentine | french   | thai |

