The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, designer, pilot
1. the pilot is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the fan of metal is the pilot##1
3. the designer is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
4. the pilot is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | rock | d&b | metal |
| Job     | designer     | dancer   | pilot        |

