.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, reading
House: wooden, farmhouse, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading  | puzzles | fishing   |
| House         | farmhouse | futuristic   | wooden |

