.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
City: prague, venice, new-york
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, sports
1. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to venice and the person watching musical movies##2
2. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| City   | venice | new-york | prague |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie    | sports  | musical   |

