2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | cola  | soy-milk     | tea |
| City   | san-francisco | edinburgh | venice    |

