2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the manager##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Job          | doctor | manager | electrician  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | documentary  | zombie |

