2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Cigar   | vegafina | tiparillo | pall-mall    |
