.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, fanta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, zombie, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage         | fanta | almond-milk   | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | action | thriller      |

