.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, hip-hop, disco
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, chess, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
2. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | r&b | hip-hop | disco |
| Hobby   | chess   | camping          | drawing |

