.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: snooker, go, poker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, aristoff, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Game     | go  | poker   | snooker |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | aristoff | havana       |

 